    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/3d8f656408fae27bef7bb7b86bdb0704.avif?t=1755592509\" width=1600 height=100 /></span><br>请记住，Skatehouse 是商店模拟器的简化版本，没有顾客四处走动，只有建立自己的小型滑板店的乐趣。预计游戏时间为 4-5 小时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/6e80eb1ff8cd5d93a786e6cfe445bb63.poster.avif?t=1755592509\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/6e80eb1ff8cd5d93a786e6cfe445bb63.webm?t=1755592509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/8799bb81b75ddc88568c6533f65642fc.poster.avif?t=1755592509\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/8799bb81b75ddc88568c6533f65642fc.webm?t=1755592509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/8799bb81b75ddc88568c6533f65642fc.mp4?t=1755592509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/2fdbe43938f787095802a111c9881b73.avif?t=1755592509\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras_big/2fdbe43938f787095802a111c9881b73.avif?t=1755592509 width=800 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计并定制你梦想中的滑板店，选择要展示的产品，管理单独的滑板零件。升级供应链，生产更多滑板，保证库存充足。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/69de6a9b28430e9281c328cdd5b955a4.poster.avif?t=1755592509\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/69de6a9b28430e9281c328cdd5b955a4.webm?t=1755592509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/69de6a9b28430e9281c328cdd5b955a4.mp4?t=1755592509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/ac49d0452f0bafd1326c8ce09be9b02b.avif?t=1755592509\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras_big/ac49d0452f0bafd1326c8ce09be9b02b.avif?t=1755592509 width=800 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组合不同零件并出售完成的滑板。解锁新型滑板来满足顾客的需要，把生意越做越大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/653b739bc3760b2a49cf4092bd01e072.poster.avif?t=1755592509\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/653b739bc3760b2a49cf4092bd01e072.webm?t=1755592509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/653b739bc3760b2a49cf4092bd01e072.mp4?t=1755592509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/ba585277bbce7878aa1a1014622fa3b4.avif?t=1755592509\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras_big/ba585277bbce7878aa1a1014622fa3b4.avif?t=1755592509 width=800 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请记住，Skatehouse 是商店模拟器的简化版本，没有顾客四处走动，只有建立自己的小型滑板店的乐趣。预计游戏时间为 4-5 小时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/c89eb0f1b74d0db162d7947a981ecd0a.avif?t=1755592509\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras_big/c89eb0f1b74d0db162d7947a981ecd0a.webp?t=1755592509 width=1600 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras/65029a8cdc2938135228930cea8c10c5.avif?t=1755592509\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153020/extras_big/65029a8cdc2938135228930cea8c10c5.avif?t=1755592509 width=800 height=50 /></span></p>",
